\c 9
\p (in
\v 1 Regai kufara, imi Isiraeri, muchifa‑
\s risisa samarudzi avanhu; nokuti ma‑
\s kapata, muchisiya Mwari wenyu; makada
\s mubayiro wokufeva pamapuriro ose
\p ezviyo.
\v 2 Buriro nechisviniro chewaini hazvingavagutsi, waini ichavanyengera.
\v 3 Havangagari munyika yaJehovha; asi Efuremu achadzokera Ijipiti, vachadya zvokudya zvine tsvina paAsiria.
\v 4 Havangadiriri Jehovha waini, zvibayiro zvavo hazvingamufadzi; zvibayiro zvavo zvichaita kwavari sezvokudya zvavanochema; vose, vanozvidya, vachasvibiswa, nokuti zvokudya zvavo ndezvavo zvoga, hazvingasviki muimba yaJehovha. S Muchabateiko nezuva reungano dzakatarwa, nezuva remitambo yaJehovha?
\v 6 Nokuti tarirai, vakabva nokuda kwokuparadzwa, asi vaIjipiti vachavaunganidza, veMemifisi vachavaviga; rukato ruchavatorera zvinhu zvavo zvesirivha zvinofadza; minzwa ichava mumatende avo.
\p
\v 7 "Mazuva okurohwa asvika, mazuva okutsiva asvika; Isiraeri vachazviziva; muporofita ibenzi, munhu anomweya anopenga, nemhaka yokuwanda kwezvakaipa zvenyu, uye nokuti ruvengo rukuru.
\v 8 Efuremu mushori kuna Mwari wangu; kana ari muporofita, rugombe rwomuteyi weshiri ruri rnunzira dzake dzose, noruvengo muimba yaMwari wake.
\p
\v 9 "Vakazvishatisa zvikuru kwazvo, sapamazuva eGibhea; acharangarira zvakaipa zvavo, achavarova pamusoro pezvivi zvavo.
\p
\v 10 "Ndakawana Isiraeri vakaita samadzambiringa murenje; ndakaona madzibaba enyu vakaita sezvibereko zvakatanga kuibva pamuonde panguva yawo yokubereka yokutanga; asi vakasvika paBhaaripeori, vakazviisa kunezvinonyadzisa, vakaitwa zvinonyangadza vachifanana nezvaidikanwa navo.
\p
\v 11 "Kana vari Efuremu, kukudzwa kwavo kuchabhururuka seshiri; kubereka hakungavipo, kana kukurirwa, kana kunaka pamuviri.
\v 12 Kunyange vakarera vana vavo, ndichavatorera ivo, kusvikira kusisina munhu; zvirokwazvo, vachava nenhamowo, kana ini ndavasiya."
\p
\v 13 Sezvandakatsaura Tire, Efuremu vakasimwa pakanaka; asi Efuremu vachabudisira muurayi vana vavo.
\v 14 Chivapai, Jehovha muchavapeiko? Chivapai
\s zvizvaro zvmoshaya namazamu asina mukaka.
\p
\v 15 "Zvakaipa zvavo zvose zviri paGirigari, nokuti ndipo pandakavavenga; nemhaka yezvakaipa zvavanoita ndichavadzinga paimba yangu, handichavadi; machinda avo ose akandimukira.
\v 16 Efuremu varohwa, mudzi wavo waoma, havangazobereki zvibereko; zvirokwazvo, kunyange vakabereka, ndichavauraya vadikanwa vakaberekwa nezvizvaro zvavo."
\v 17 Mwari wangu achavarasha, nokuti havana kumunzwa; vachava vadzungairi pakati pamarudzi avanhu.
